sequenceDiagram
  participant F as Frontend Chat UI
  participant G as Gateway
  participant CS as Chat Service
  participant US as User Service
  participant FS as Forum Service
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant RD as Redis

  F->>G: GET /api/chat/groups/:groupId/messages
  G->>CS: forward request
  CS->>US: verify token
  US-->>CS: userId
  CS->>FS: membership check for group/forum
  FS-->>CS: member allowed
  CS->>DB: query Message by groupId
  CS->>RD: publish/subscribe events (realtime path)
  CS-->>F: message list
